* software.iso contains software licensed under various licenses that permit redistribution in unmodified form written by other people. I have included them because one of the more time consuming parts of getting this working was finding all the right versions that played nice with each other.
* all files in the grammar directory are in the public domain, except for multiedit.txt/py , which i adapted from a post on the Dragonfly forums (which was itself adapted from dragonfly-modules). it is released under the LGPL. This is noted at the top of the file.
* the files under util are also released under the LGPL
